{"parentUuid":"20018542-bfb3-4e19-893e-f6cb889d8054","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_0197nnoio7PhRrbHHyFE3HbC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to save context/conversation history in Claude Code so it persists across computer restarts.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":88,"cache_read_input_tokens":32189,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":88,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":10}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"ca25e023-f481-49b3-888e-dcbe154e4843","timestamp":"2026-04-08T02:09:01.471Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\project\\info-gitlab\\oa","sessionId":"39eddcd2-6187-4739-bea8-d0fd1d99f01d","version":"2.1.78","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"ca25e023-f481-49b3-888e-dcbe154e4843","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_0197nnoio7PhRrbHHyFE3HbC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"操，这个问题简单，爹听好了：\n\n## Claude Code 的上下文保存方式\n\nClaude Code 的**对话上下文本身不会跨会话持久化**——你关了终端/重启电脑，对话就没了。但有几种方式可以保留关键信息：\n\n### 1. 自动记忆文件（已经在用了）\n你的项目里已经配了 `CLAUDE.md` 文件，这些每次对话都会自动加载。重要的东西可以让我写进去。\n\n我还有个持久记忆目录：`~/.claude/projects/.../memory/`，写进去的内容也会自动加载。\n\n### 2. 恢复上一次对话\n```bash\nclaude --resume        # 选择一个历史对话继续\nclaude --continue      # 直接继续最近一次对话\n```\n这个**不需要电脑不重启**，重启后也能用，历史对话是存在磁盘上的。\n\n### 3. 把重要上下文写进 CLAUDE.md\n你觉得哪些信息每次都要用到，直接跟我说\"记住这个\"，我写进 `CLAUDE.md` 或记忆文件里，下次新对话自动生效。\n\n---\n\n**总结：用 `claude --continue` 或 `claude --resume` 就能恢复之前的对话，重启电脑也没问题。** 长期要记住的东西让我写进 CLAUDE.md 就行。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":88,"cache_read_input_tokens":32189,"output_tokens":466,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":88},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"ac6b26eb-754f-45de-bb08-2f0e46a3ccbf","timestamp":"2026-04-08T02:09:04.265Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\project\\info-gitlab\\oa","sessionId":"39eddcd2-6187-4739-bea8-d0fd1d99f01d","version":"2.1.78","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
