{"parentUuid":"9775ca64-8f33-4b7e-a67d-d2d0a63bc19e","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_0138FEE17t2xP53g1wqHqYrV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n啊操，你是说你之前开了4个窗口，`--continue` 不知道接哪个对吧？\n\n用这个：\n\n```bash\nclaude --resume\n```\n\n它会**列出所有历史对话让你选**，你能看到每个对话的时间和内容摘要，选你要的那个就行。\n\n如果你想直接继续**某个特定对话**，可以用对话 ID：\n\n```bash\nclaude --resume <session-id>\n```\n\n---\n\n**总结：`--continue` 只接最近一个对话，`--resume` 可以选择任意一个历史对话恢复。4个窗口的话用 `--resume` 挑着接。**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":24,"cache_read_input_tokens":32742,"output_tokens":198,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":24},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"eb961563-9d4d-41aa-98e4-0d3332c3fd06","timestamp":"2026-04-08T02:10:22.417Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\project\\info-gitlab\\oa","sessionId":"39eddcd2-6187-4739-bea8-d0fd1d99f01d","version":"2.1.78","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
